{
  "stem": "5375.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know that that is waiting for us, because I would have remained behind, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd rather go in the Russian prison camp and come home later than never.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] This [NON-ENGLISH] was a big sugar factory, and that, what they made a concentration camp from-- from that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was no more factory, no more sugar factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the railway tracks were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The dirt carloads were there-- I mean, the empty carloads were there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We arrived there at night, and they count us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Hungarian captain gave it-- gave us over to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Gestapo didn't even understood what the captain says, because he was talking Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he took over the Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were [? demonstrated, ?] you know, like soldiers. '1, 2, 3, 4,' you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were going, you know, singing, you know, on the street, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because instead of guns, we had the utilities-- I mean, the-- the shovels, and the axes, and so on, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here, there were some old people brought from Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw, when we were staying in the line, that they were bringing out the-- the soup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the night-- dinner, a soup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there were the old people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were staying in the line with a dish, and the guy was giving them about a little soup.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was begging him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, [INAUDIBLE], do me a favor, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Friend, give me one more, a little bit more.' The Gestapo came with a stick and started hitting him over the head, and over the head, and over the head, until he spilled his soup.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he put, you know, his dish on the head.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
